<div class="artwork-content">

        <div id="artwork-image">
            <img src="../images/143273_2574162.jpg" alt="Bamboo with Chinese Yew and Deer with Maples" title="Painting attributed to Hasegawa Togaku (d.1623), Calligraphy by Tetsuzan Sodon (1531-1617)
Japanese, Bamboo with Chinese Yew and Deer with Maples"  />          </div>

    <p class="tools">
                    <a href="../artwork/191643/zoomify" class="zoomify-link"><strong>Zoom</strong> image</a><br />
